  <property name="windowTitle">
   <string>LandScan Population Modelling</string>
  </property>

  <!--
    Page indices (stacked widget order):
      0  – Mode selector          (shared entry point)
      1  – ROI                    (shared)
      2  – Model selection        (Train & Run only)
      3  – Weights upload         (Run Existing only)
      4  – Hyperparameters        (shared; auto-filled + locked in Run Existing)
      5  – Loss function          (Train & Run only)
      6  – Time frame             (shared)
      7  – Output directory       (shared)

    Run Existing flow : 0 → 1 → 3 → 4 → 6 → 7
    Train & Run flow  : 0 → 1 → 2 → 4 → 5 → 6 → 7
  -->

